{
  "id": "fdd3411ccc24abd5",
  "fields": {
    "apply_url": "https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/skelar/ef8fd5bb-76de-430d-be61-ed51f406c40f/application",
    "company": "skelar",
    "compensation": "",
    "content_hash": "fdd3411ccc24abd5",
    "department": "Operations",
    "description": "[https://app.ashbyhq.com/api/images/user-content/586ac3cb-f234-40cf-96fd-3daae8c41309/3a2721ac-0cf6-4bb5-a785-483b8d1018c3/Ashby_header.png]\n\nHi! We are Liven — a self-discovery platform that helps people better understand themselves and transform their lives.\n\nAt Liven, we empower coaches to build and grow their private practice without the hassle of administrative work. Our platform connects you with engaged clients, provides advanced digital tools, and offers full support — so you can focus on what truly matters: helping people on their self-discovery journey.\n\nInside our ecosystem:\n\n— Self-discovery platform — a space where users work on burnout, anxiety, relationship challenges, and personal growth through guided content and coaching.\n\n— Online Coaching — personalized support from coaches helping clients navigate complex life situations and build healthier habits.\n\n— Digital Tools — including text coaching, video sessions, shared content, and goal tracking to support long-term transformation.\n\nLiven is growing rapidly, and we are expanding our global network of coaches across all time zones.\n\nWe are looking for a Wellness Coach at Liven. In this role, you will support clients through meaningful life challenges and help them build sustainable changes in their behavior, mindset, and lifestyle.\n\n🎯 How Will You Make An Impact?\n— Provide personalized coaching through text messaging using our digital tools.\n— Support clients dealing with burnout, anxiety, relationship challenges, and other behavioral difficulties.\n— Guide users by tailoring in-app content and recommending relevant services.\n— Collaborate with the Liven team to create and launch workshops, webinars, and new coaching content.\n\n✨Why this is exciting?\n— Consistent Client Flow: a steady stream of engaged clients through our platform.\n— No Extra Admin Work: we handle acquisition, scheduling and operations.\n— Flexible Schedule: set your own working hours, including weekdays and weekends.\n— Diversified Experience: work with clients from around the world facing a variety of challenges.\n— Ongoing Support \u0026 Growth: grow your career within a supportive and evolving coaching community.\n\n🧩 What Makes You a Perfect Fit?\n— 1+ years of coaching experience.\n— Proven experience working with stress, burnout, anxiety, relationships, or similar topics.\n— Strong written and verbal communication skills in English.\n— Stable internet connection and a computer with camera and audio.\n— Availability to work across different time zones (weekends are a plus).\n— Completed all screening questions.\n\n💪🏻What will you enjoy most about being at Liven?\n— Technology-Driven Platform: advanced tools that go beyond basic video sessions.\n— Global Reach: work with clients from all over the world.\n— Privacy \u0026 Security: state-of-the-art encrypted communication tools.\n— Professional Growth: continuous support and opportunities to develop as a coach.\n\nStill on Day 1: A Constant Expansion\n\nWe are scaling fast and building a global coaching network. If you’re passionate about helping people and want a flexible, meaningful coaching career — let’s connect.\n\nFuel your curiosity at Liven 🔎\n\n[https://app.ashbyhq.com/api/images/user-content/586ac3cb-f234-40cf-96fd-3daae8c41309/bf8afb62-59f5-436b-b500-74f06bd0bb6e/Ashby_footer_eng.png]",
